Module com.sun.xml.bind
Package com.sun.xml.bind.v2.runtime

Class MarshallerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.xml.bind.helpers.AbstractMarshallerImpl
      • com.sun.xml.bind.v2.runtime.MarshallerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Marshaller, ValidationEventHandler
    public final class MarshallerImpl
extends AbstractMarshallerImpl
implements ValidationEventHandler
    Implementation of Marshaller interface for the JAXB RI.

    Eventually all the marshal(java.lang.Object, java.io.OutputStream, javax.xml.namespace.NamespaceContext) methods call into the write(com.sun.xml.bind.v2.runtime.Name, com.sun.xml.bind.v2.runtime.JaxBeanInfo<T>, T, com.sun.xml.bind.v2.runtime.output.XmlOutput, java.lang.Runnable) method.

    Author:
    Kohsuke Kawaguchi, Vivek Pandey
